<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>后台管理 - 我的个人博客</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="admin-layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-header">
        <a href="/" class="admin-brand-mark gradient-button" aria-label="Poppis">
          <span class="gradient-text">Poppis</span>
        </a>
        <div>
          <p class="admin-kicker">Content Studio</p>
          <h2>后台管理</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <nav class="sidebar-nav">
        <a href="/poppis-console/dashboard" class="nav-item active">仪表盘</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/posts" class="nav-item">文章管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/categories" class="nav-item">分类管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/tags" class="nav-item">标签管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/about" class="nav-item">关于我</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/logout" class="nav-item logout">退出登录</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="admin-main">
      <div class="admin-header">
        <div>
          <p class="admin-kicker">Dashboard</p>
          <h1>仪表盘</h1>
          <p class="admin-lead">欢迎回来，<%= user.username %>。今天适合整理选题、检查归档，然后继续发布新内容。</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/poppis-console/posts/new" class="btn btn-primary">新建文章</a>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-icon">P</span>
          <div class="stat-info">
            <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.posts %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">文章总数</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-icon">C</span>
          <div class="stat-info">
            <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.categories %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">分类总数</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-icon">T</span>
          <div class="stat-info">
            <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.tags %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">标签总数</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-split-grid">
        <section class="quick-actions">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <p class="admin-kicker">Workflow</p>
              <h2>快速操作</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="section-note">常用入口集中到一起，减少切换成本。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/poppis-console/posts/new" class="btn btn-primary">写新文章</a>
            <a href="/poppis-console/categories" class="btn btn-secondary">整理分类</a>
            <a href="/poppis-console/tags" class="btn btn-secondary">维护标签</a>
            <a href="/poppis-console/about" class="btn btn-secondary">更新关于页</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="admin-note-panel">
          <p class="admin-kicker">Studio Note</p>
          <h2>把后台也做成一个内容创作界面。</h2>
          <p>现在这套后台不只是管理页，而更像内容工作台。你可以从这里规划结构、整理主题，再把文章发布到前台的编辑式首页。</p>
          <div class="admin-note-pills">
            <span>Editorial</span>
            <span>Glass</span>
            <span>Gradient</span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
